- Loops: `for (const item of items)`, `items.reduce` (iteration) = 2 loops x 5 = 10
- Assignments: `followUpMultiplier = ...`, `loyaltyMultiplier = ...`, `basePremium = ...`, `insuranceSum = ...`, `remainingCap = ...` = 5 assignments x 6 = 30

